Sets to Install and run the program

First we need to install all the updates for the Pox controller

Run the topology code (1.py)
This creates the topology

Now in different terminal the Iperf commands in all the 4 terminal with the basic controller

Now we could see that bandthwidth is same

Now start the controller(controller2.py) in different terminal.

Post that open 4 hosts with xterm h1 h2 h3 h4

Now run the iperf and we can see that bandwidth is shared according to the priorities set in the controller
